list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment: - refactor context - now a unique context object is created for each graph object during creation - fixed a bug in the context system

task.summary: Default task
- support for exporting the following elements: BinaryView MLIL Function MLIL Basic Block MLIL Instruction MLIL Expression
- added some debug info
Refactor in order to first dump BV to CSV file
CSV dumping - no threading support
added support for relationships
added support for relationships
- Fixed various bugs in CSV dumping - support the neo4j import csv tool
- Major improvements to performance
- Fixed some parsing bugs with Branch relationships - Fixed a collision between Var and Expression object labels
- Fixed some bugs with variable parsing
- Testing parallelism

- Massive performance improvements - Refactor UUID_Generator class to use internal neo4j apoc procedure - Addressed multi-threading locking issues when competing for the same relationship nodes for insertions
- Fixed handling of Transient Error and lock
- Fixed some problems with BasicBlock branching - Added a Configuration file - Added comments to the code - Added plugin.json
- Fixed an issue with MLIL_SET_VAR not being cached correctly
- Version 1.0 - Fixed a major issue with relationship creation within the DB

- Version 1.1 - Added "Data" nodes, currently supporting Constant nodes that are pointers to strings - Fixed a problem with correctly identifying Constant nodes - Started adding support for Diaphora implementation

- Version 1.2 - Refactor project structure - Added CSV Post Processing capabilities: * Data Symbols and String pointers - Added Function call relationships (call instruction pointing to the called function)
- Added Def\Use chains
- Added initial support for Type enrichment, using clang pre-processor on a header file
- working on integrating type data from a parsed header into the binary view automatically
- Complete refactor of the header parsing module: * now uses neo4j bolt driver instead of py2neo * extreme performance improvement - Working on defining the type definition tree for a given type
- refactor header processing module
- bug fixes on node handlers
- Added feature: define all known function in a binary view with full type information
- Major bug fixes in the way BasicBlocks were parsed
- A function call expression will not have sub expression representing the argument list for that function call
- Work on Flow Analysis module
